
<p>Simple single-page website with (a) reasons to leave Substack; (b) links to comprehensive step-by-step instructions for how to move to other platforms, such as <a href="https://ghost.org/">Ghost</a>, <a href="https://buttondown.com/">Buttondown</a>, and <a href="https://www.beehiiv.com/">Beehiiv</a>; and (c) links to <a href="https://www.citationneeded.news/">several</a> <a href="https://www.platformer.news/">popular</a> <a href="https://garbageday.substack.com/p/its-time-to-leave-substack">publications</a> that moved and are <a href="https://randsinrepose.com/archives/welcome-to-ghost">glad they did</a>.</p>

